                    <BitTypography Variant="BitTypographyVariant.H5" Gutter>Quality</BitTypography>
                    <BitTypography Variant="BitTypographyVariant.Body1">
                        We expertly execute our work, utilizing innovation and ingenuity to provide high-quality services and products.
                    </BitTypography>
                </div>

                <div class="value-card">
                    <BitTypography Variant="BitTypographyVariant.H5" Gutter>Integrity</BitTypography>
                    <BitTypography Variant="BitTypographyVariant.Body1">
                        Conduct our business in a legal and ethical manner, build lasting relationships through honesty, respect and trust with our employees as well as our business partners.
                    </BitTypography>
                </div>

                <div class="value-card">
                    <BitTypography Variant="BitTypographyVariant.H5" Gutter>Transparency</BitTypography>
                    <BitTypography Variant="BitTypographyVariant.Body1">
                        Being honest and open when communicating with our employees and business partners.
                    </BitTypography>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

